column2: More than 50 amazon workers at MSP1 in Shakopee, MN walked off the job just after 12am this morning to protest the elimination of unpaid time off, unsafe conditions, & the appearance of retaliation against workers who speak out.   Here's Hafsa Hasan, one of the leaders: https://t.co/dO9ckCrxsJ
